data.description: This 2,382 square foot home sits on a beautiful 1.86 acre lot and features 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. The main level has a great layout with the bedrooms and main living area. The lower level has room for additional bedrooms or office area as needed. Or finish it for in home theatre room or mancave. The property offers the best of both worlds in a desirable location. It is minutes away from the village, however it sits in a rural setting with a gorgeous view.
